    <p class="text-text-muted text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
      Coding agents are getting powerful fast. The tooling to actually run them at scale? Nonexistent.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-lg bg-bg-card border border-border">
